## Non-goals

- A pointer, not a substitute for human review, SAST, SCA, secrets scanning, or CI checks.
- MCP tool descriptions are untrusted text (MCP spec) — verify against the skill source if a rule looks wrong.
- Full inlined bodies: `secure-vibe dev regenerate --full-inline`.
